'''''Instant Adventures''''' is a ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' book published by [[West End Games]] in [[1997]]. The adventures within are described as taking place between the events of [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']].

